rComments: Présence en classe très fortement conseillée... il donne les slides ou documents PDF mais toute l'information importante est communiquée en classe. Il répond aux questions assez clairement et est capable de garder l'attention des étudiants. Il exige que l'ordinateur soit utilisé pour les notes seulement. un bon prof en général!

Does not let you use computer to take notes in class. Refuses to respond to e-mails so you can only ask questions in class. Funny prof but goes through material very fast. Exams do not reflect what was taught in class. Not sure if he even writes his own exams... Doesn't review his slides before class. Interesting material but not very well taught.
